oor Area Ratio (FAR) for commercial properties outside heritage sectors, aiming to double it in Industrial Area Phase I and II to 2.0. This move, pending approval from top officials, also involves potential revisions to coverage areas and building heights to boost commercial space and urban development.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/chandigarh-administration-considers-doubling-far-for-commercial-properties/129993623?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-200720/129993623.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}]}